Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.07,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,#11 The story of Banmon, part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? And those arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you gonna thank us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for him, that samurai there \Nwould be monster meat by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not who you are, \Nbut thank you for saving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The villagers can live in peace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's blind so he sees with his soul. \N-He's blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He can fight like that \Nwith no sight or arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how amazing he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's beaten monsters left and right \Ntraveling this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And not some tiny little ghouls, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We only go after the real deal, \Ndemons and monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, we heard there's \Na rich province nearby. Know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be our Lord Daigo's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll reach the city limits \Nin half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Daigo's land, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He was dressed well, so he might be \Nsome important guy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, sir. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is my fault for underestimating \Nthat monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't lose to anybody in the dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But a real fight is a different matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That in itself is a futile argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A vagabond and the heir to this land \Ncannot be compared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some fresh vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all fine goods. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby demon has been born, red all over
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we feed it to the mountain beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we feed it to the ocean creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrap it up, send it adrift,  \N now it's out of sight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the demon! The demon child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon child has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Hyakkimaru, rice balls! \NAnd made with white rice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need more than one day \Nto see all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, they're putting on a play \Nover there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For years on end,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,demons have tortured our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As the lord of this land
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Daigo Kagemitsu, \Nshall now slay this demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great Goddess of Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Daigo's people \Nwith your benevolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do protect our lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's pretty awesome, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"That guy"? How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Lord Daigo Kagemitsu, \Nthe man who made our land so rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just like you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon has been defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All foes who defy me will be vanquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And my domain will be protected \Nfor eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \NI'm sorry for what happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come here \Nbecause of the rumors, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This land is like none other \Nin these hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious as to \Nwhat was blessing this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the demons that Daigo defeated \Nare enshrined up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going up there to check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We got no business for \Nsome long dead monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only after the live ones, \Nthe raging ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've killed humans as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But dang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's nothing for us to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a bit more fun here \Nand then go on to the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I say it's the curse of Banmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that's why it hasn't rained at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh, you shouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The villages I passed through \Nwere all dry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues, then this fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. Lord Daigo's land \Nis protected by the Goddess of Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but ever since those things \Nstarted up at Banmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Asakura's been acting suspicious, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that Banmon thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? A blind boy with no arms? \N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe one of his legs \Nis a prosthetic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they travel, defeating monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've died if he had not saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They bragged that they were only after \Nstrong demon gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And he really did slay a huge monster \Nwith just one slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be a fort  \N that protected us from the Asakura clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a fierce battle, \Nand all except one wall got burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was the first time  \N Daigo's army drove the Asakuras away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kagemitsu's influence grew from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a tall wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the Goddess of Mercy that  \N Lord Daigo's wife prays to dwells in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently the Asakuras  \N have been getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They shoot Daigo's men  \N and spies onto the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to sully  \N the Goddess of Mercy's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghouls have been gathering nightly,  \N attracted to those corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody goes near it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say it might even be cursed  \N by the demons Lord Daigo defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you sense something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful. \NIf you cross that wall, you'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're just a kid. \NDon't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See that? They're Asakura sentries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they catch you, \Nthey'll shoot you onto Banmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to find here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go rob corpses someplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we're here for. \NWe're going to beat Banmon's monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This used to be where our village was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They came barging in \Nand built that Banmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My home is on the other side! \NLet go, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Asakura territory now. \NYou'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa... Mama... Mama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone abandoned the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I ain't giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cross Banmon someday and get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-We'll help. \N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Asakura army \Nkeeps watch during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy? It's even worse at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never seen the likes of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huge monsters everywhere... \N-Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My bro can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You meant it about beating the monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually don't do it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you fed us, so it's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dororo. This is Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sukeroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My son really is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, the lord is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow anybody \Nto interfere with my prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-You think we should go unpunished? \N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing the life \Nof an innocent child...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We will pay for what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We may already be paying for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying I should've let \Nmy land rot in hell as it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, is it truly the well-being \Nof your people that you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Or to defeat other domains \Nand become a great lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, our son...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Women don't understand politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ASAKURA DOMAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Daigo Kagemitsu did? \N-He left an hour ago with a small troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like a joyride, \Nand he wished to keep it secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See? The Asakura sentries are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So hey, Sukeroku. What's your mama like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's plump with white skin. \NThe prettiest in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-She makes the best rice cakes too. \N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we meet her, you can have some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fox fire sprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Banmon monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we really can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called all the foxes around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru! You stupid fox, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk, you idiot! Take this, and this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Sukeroku! It's dangerous to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bro. \N-Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rash, Sukeroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A traveling boy with a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's about my age or a bit older.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you haven't paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Young Master! \N-Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He must still be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are you going to do \Nif you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You said my father was shocked \Nwhen he heard your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Father must know something about his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Father and Mother's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the baby disappeared to \N16 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy might have the answer \Nto all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby demon has been born, red all over
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we feed it to the mountain beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, you there. \N-Young Master, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon child...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:20:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon child has come back \Nto destroy Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukeroku, Sukeroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sukeroku! \N-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukeroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "demon child"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And "destroy Daigo"? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Answer me! \N-Young Master, do not listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the curse of the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The demons ate the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Its arms, legs, nose, \Nmouth, skin, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They ate everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the child's come back \Nto return the curse to Daigo and his land!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish  \N indifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes,  \N I lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope  \N in the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade...  \N until night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming  \N of a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kyubi"
